name: BOO!! POW!!
description:
BABY ON ROAD-PLAY series

BOO and POW, are adorable twins who are alike in almost every possible way.
The next door neighbor to STICKY BRAIN is a twin who, along with his sister POW, loves to eat anything she finds in the backyard. and BOO loves to smashing it first before he eat like soup. 
But now, they are preparing for halloween partyyyy
